     6

    12

    14	- Replace all strict version pins in `pyproject.toml` with flexible versioning.
    15	- Run `poetry update` to update the lockfile accordingly.
    16	- Save all changes and make sure `tree-sitter` and `zope-interface` follow the new policy.
